Premium League is a fantasy sports game that lets you to choose the world's greatest stars on your team and score based on their performance in real games. You can create leagues with your friends and show who is the best besides participating in premium leagues in which everyone is already in.

In Premium League, you:
- Choose one team per round;
- Can participate in several championships around the world;
- Can choose substitutes;
- Choose a captain to double your score;
- See live match statistics for the round;

